{"tid":657764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保護廣東話既其中一個關鍵，係親友間就算有人唔識廣東話，都照繼續講","createTime":"2018-05-08T11:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T05:41:52.000Z","uid":48083,"like":81,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"87ced53bf735f502d95827dfa4a5621efa32f77e","tid":657764,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T11:17:46.000Z","msg":"發覺好多時係，一大班人，<br />\n當中有一個淨係識蝗語，<br />\n然後全部人由於唔好意思定點，<br />\n自動全部講哂蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是乎，一班親友入面有一兩個蝗語人<br />\n就全部講蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n查實落得香港既蝗人90%聽得明廣東話<br />\n正確做法應該照講廣東話<br />\n最多佢唔明先個別講解吓<br />\n<br />\n嗰point係，當有一些認識，非敵對既蝗語人喺生活圈入面，<br />\n邊個就邊個，就睇邊個夠堅持（或霸道，無賴）講自己既語言，要人地就佢<br />\n而哩方面，蝗語人通常贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3095299209e6bb9722db935452c1d0780b0a94bb","tid":657764,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T11:22:39.000Z","msg":"因為佢哋覺得唔識粵語係正常<br />\n識狗話係必然"},{"pid":"51d9b993e197254aceb5585a264b47000487ee64","tid":657764,"uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"3095299209e6bb9722db935452c1d0780b0a94bb","tid":657764,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T11:22:39.000Z","msg":"因為佢哋覺得唔識粵語係正常<br />\n識狗話係必然"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T11:28:29.000Z","msg":"所以要企硬<br />\n最多佢講蝗語我用廣東話<br />\n<br />\n因為吓吓比人一個頂十個<br />\n就算蝗語人係少數可以洗走廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99bed593119a9ce4f098d2d88ff8f8f3445a2da","tid":657764,"uid":176366,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T13:17:34.000Z","msg":"冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\